                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-130-off651 t18170917-130-cd652"></join>, two watches, value 2l. 10s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18170917-130-victim928" type="victimName">
                        Luke 
                        Court
                     <interp inst="t18170917-130-victim928" type="surname" value="Court"></interp>
